ning_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1693478271 320w" width="2208" height="1692" alt="Is the Care Certificate required for staff induction - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Is the Care Certificate required for staff induction - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-23_"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-8777" data-category="Generic Content" data-name="Matcha" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dBFCZX khzvmY pf-24_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-gvPcJq dRaLso"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-25_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-26_"><p class="sc-eONOlN cfGtgs pf-27_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-29_">The question of whether the Care Certificate is required for staff induction is a nuanced one. While the Care Certificate itself is not a mandatory requirement, it is highly recommended and expected by the Care Quality Commission (CQC) for staff who are new to regulated services to achieve the competencies outlined in the <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/products/care-certificate-train-the-trainer-trainer-pack-cpduk-accredited?variant=31839814582341" target="_blank"><i><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);">Care Certificate</span></i></a> as part of their induction.</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-fUklNj thmnJ pf-30_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-32_">The framework of the Care Certificate</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_framework_of_the_Care_Certificate_-_Staff_Induction_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1693478361" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_framework_of_the_Care_Certificate_-_Staff_Induction_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1693478361 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_framework_of_the_Care_Certificate_-_Staff_Induction_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1693478361 320w" width="2240" height="1493" alt="The framework of the Care Certificate - Staff Induction - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="The framework of the Care Certificate - Staff Induction - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-33_"/><p class="sc-eONOlN cfGtgs pf-34_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-36_">The Care Certificate provides a framework for training, education, and assessment within the health and social care sectors. It builds upon previous standards and sets out explicit learning outcomes, competencies, and standards of behaviour that are expected of new healthcare support workers and adult social care workers (HCSW/ASCW). </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-fUklNj thmnJ pf-37_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-39_">Complementing a comprehensive induction program </span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Complementing_a_comprehensive_induction_program_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1693478433" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Complementing_a_comprehensive_induction_program_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1693478433 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Complementing_a_comprehensive_induction_program_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1693478433 320w" width="1831" height="1220" alt="Complementing a comprehensive induction program - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Complementing a comprehensive induction program - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-40_"/><p class="sc-eONOlN cfGtgs pf-41_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-43_">It is important to note that the Care Certificate is 